@host = http://localhost:5400

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Note: gRPC endpoints require an HTTP/2 gRPC client (not REST).
### Use the ProtobuffEncoder.Demo.Grpc.Client console app or grpcurl.
###
### Services:
###   Weather/GetForecast       — Unary
###   Weather/StreamForecasts   — Server streaming
###   Chat/Chat                 — Duplex streaming
###   Chat/SendNotification     — Unary
